{"surah":104,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"104:1","arabic":" وَيْلٌ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُّمَزَةٍ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","id":"Celakalah bagi setiap pengumpat dan pencela,","words":[{"a":"وَيْلٌۭ","en":"Woe","id":"kecelakaan"},{"a":"لِّكُلِّ","en":"to every","id":"bagi setiap"},{"a":"هُمَزَةٍۢ","en":"slanderer","id":"pengumpat"},{"a":"لُّمَزَةٍ","en":"backbiter","id":"pencela"}]},{"n":2,"key":"104:2","arabic":"ٱلَّذِى جَمَعَ مَالًا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it.","id":"yang mengumpulkan harta dan menghitung-hitungnya,","words":[{"a":"ٱلَّذِى","en":"The one who","id":"yang"},{"a":"جَمَعَ","en":"collects","id":"mengumpulkan"},{"a":"مَالًۭا","en":"wealth","id":"harta"},{"a":"وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","en":"and counts it","id":"dan dia menghitungnya"}]},{"n":3,"key":"104:3","arabic":"يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخْلَدَهُۥ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal.","id":"dia (manusia) mengira bahwa hartanya itu dapat mengekalkannya.","words":[{"a":"يَحْسَبُ","en":"Thinking","id":"dia mengira"},{"a":"أَنَّ","en":"that","id":"bahwasanya"},{"a":"مَالَهُۥٓ","en":"his wealth","id":"hartanya"},{"a":"أَخْلَدَهُۥ","en":"will make him immortal","id":"mengekalkannya"}]},{"n":4,"key":"104:4","arabic":"كَلَّا ۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِى ٱلْحُطَمَةِ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher.","id":"Sekali-kali tidak! Pasti dia akan dilemparkan ke dalam (neraka) Ḥuṭamah.","words":[{"a":"كَلَّا ۖ","en":"Nay","id":"sekali-kali tidak"},{"a":"لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ","en":"Surely he will be thrown","id":"sungguh dia akan dilemparkan"},{"a":"فِى","en":"in","id":"dalam"},{"a":"ٱلْحُطَمَةِ","en":"the Crusher","id":"Hutamah"}]},{"n":5,"key":"104:5","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْحُطَمَةُ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher?","id":"Dan tahukah kamu apakah (neraka) Ḥuṭamah itu?","words":[{"a":"وَمَآ","en":"And what","id":"dan apakah"},{"a":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","en":"will make you know","id":"kamu tahu"},{"a":"مَا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"ٱلْحُطَمَةُ","en":"the Crusher (is)","id":"Hutamah"}]},{"n":6,"key":"104:6","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلْمُوقَدَةُ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"It is the fire of Allāh, [eternally] fueled,","id":"(Yaitu) api (azab) Allah yang dinyalakan,","words":[{"a":"نَارُ","en":"A Fire","id":"api"},{"a":"ٱللَّهِ","en":"Allah","id":"Allah"},{"a":"ٱلْمُوقَدَةُ","en":"kindled","id":"dinyalakan"}]},{"n":7,"key":"104:7","arabic":"ٱلَّتِى تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلْأَفْـِٔدَةِ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"Which mounts directed at the hearts.","id":"yang (membakar) sampai ke hati.","words":[{"a":"ٱلَّتِى","en":"Which","id":"yang"},{"a":"تَطَّلِعُ","en":"mounts up","id":"naik"},{"a":"عَلَى","en":"to","id":"ke atas/sampai"},{"a":"ٱلْأَفْـِٔدَةِ","en":"the hearts","id":"hati"}]},{"n":8,"key":"104:8","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيْهِم مُّؤْصَدَةٌ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"Indeed, it [i.e., Hellfire] will be closed down upon them","id":"Sungguh, api itu ditutup rapat atas (diri) mereka,","words":[{"a":"إِنَّهَا","en":"Indeed, it","id":"sesungguhnya ia (api)"},{"a":"عَلَيْهِم","en":"(will be) upon them","id":"atas mereka"},{"a":"مُّؤْصَدَةٌۭ","en":"closed over","id":"terikat/ditutup rapat"}]},{"n":9,"key":"104:9","arabic":"فِى عَمَدٍ مُّمَدَّدَةٍۭ","page":601,"juz":30,"en":"In extended columns.","id":"(sedang mereka itu) diikat pada tiang-tiang yang panjang.","words":[{"a":"فِى","en":"In","id":"dalam/pada"},{"a":"عَمَدٍۢ","en":"columns","id":"tiang"},{"a":"مُّمَدَّدَةٍۭ","en":"extended","id":"panjang"}]}]}